<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Privacy Policy - Virotikly</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; max-width: 800px; margin: 40px auto; padding: 0 20px; color: #24292e; }
        h1 { color: #000; border-bottom: 1px solid #eaecef; padding-bottom: 0.3em; }
        h2 { color: #24292e; margin-top: 24px; border-bottom: 1px solid #eaecef; padding-bottom: 0.3em; }
        .date { color: #6a737d; font-style: italic; margin-bottom: 30px; }
        strong { color: #000; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p class="date">Last Updated: April 13, 2026</p>

    <p>Welcome to <strong>Virotikly</strong>. We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information.</p>

    <h2>1. Information We Access</h2>
    <p>Virotikly does not collect or store your personal data on our servers. All authentication is handled securely through <strong>TikTok’s official OAuth system</strong>. We only access the basic profile information necessary to provide our services, such as your public username and display name.</p>

    <h2>2. Use of Information</h2>
    <p>The information accessed is used solely to facilitate the features of the Virotikly platform. We do not use your data for any purposes outside of the core functionality of our website.</p>

    <h2>3. Data Sharing</h2>
    <p>We <strong>do not sell, trade, or share</strong> your information with third parties. Your data is never used for advertising, marketing, or external tracking.</p>

    <h2>4. Data Retention and Deletion</h2>
    <p>We do not maintain a permanent database of your TikTok personal information. You can revoke Virotikly's access at any time through your TikTok account security settings.</p>

    <h2>5. Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions about this Privacy Policy, please contact us at: <br>
    <strong>[virotikly@gmail.com]</strong></p>

</body>
</html>
